{
  "stem": "2684.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And if you wake me up 4 o'clock in the morning, I can't tell you in any other language but in German.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "If you asked me in Hungarian, it takes me half an hour for my mind to translate that all to English.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were Fluechtlings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That's all I know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That's a prisoner, or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It's, it's a German word which describes a bloody Jew in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we arrived to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Dachau, whatever little hair had grown out because from the lack of food, the hair had grown very, very slowly, and also in winter.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got again shaved everywhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then again, we had a shower, and they came this disinfectant stuff.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We got, again, a new stripe prison clothe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they put us into barracks, but the barracks were civilized.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two of us were sleeping one underneath, one over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rooms were clean.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were room, not barracks, stone walls, rooms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It had a special shower section, decent toilets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all we did there was lying there, doing nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we even got some food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bread, the usual food, but some, something more.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think so we got sixth of bread, a bit more butter, a bit more marmalade, and the same soup what we always get.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the food in my whole nearly year of, of imprisonment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the general menu.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no, no other stuff.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I became an adult the minute I left Auschwitz and became a worker.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it showed, that's why I think so the German, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] this, this Wehrmacht officer took a sorry on me because I was young and I was still very, very virile as far as working concerned.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
